    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.33.39-40_0001a" />
                <note type="curatorial">143-2 Aly Collection</note>
                
                
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                Skyrim Farm                 <hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT</hi>
                    <lb/>
                Route 7
                    <lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.  
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Sep. 24, '61</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Bower:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Thanks for yet another generous act in my behalf! You still surprise me, altho' it has been long since I first learned of your unselfish interest in my work. &#8212; <hi rend="underline">And</hi>, you aroused interest in Lucile!</p>
              
                <p>Things go well here. There is more publicity around here than ever &#8212; <hi rend="caps">TV</hi>, radio, talk among housewives, businessmen, students. My Epic America class is the largest yet and the new Arts and Science auditorium is tops in every way.</p>
                    
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.33.39-40_0001b"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                    
                <p>They are planning big doings in Nebraska when the bronze bust is unveiled. My visit there recently was a joy all around. It was like coming home &#8212; and that after 40 years. There seemed to be no strangeness (People <hi rend="underline">are</hi> dear.)</p>
                
                <p>I know you are going like a dynamo, as usual. I do marvel at your tremendous industry. I admire it too, but I do like to think of the few times we've been together with maybe a bit of O-Be-Joyful handy and nothing at all to do but be happy friends.</p>
                
                <note type="authorial">(inside)</note>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">39</fw>
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.33.39-40_0002"/>
                <fw type="authorial">-3-</fw>
                
                <closer>
                <salute>With affectionate thoughts as always,</salute>
                <signed>John N.</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
                
                
                
